translations: v.生成螯合物（chelate 的第三人称单数）

sentences.sentence: The oscillator strength of the chelates are 2 to 5 times higher than that of free ions.
sentences.translation: 等离子的配合物有超灵敏跃迁，其振子强度比自由离子高2 ~ 5倍。

sentences.sentence: Under ultimate condition, CM CTS chelates and flocculates Cu 2+ up to an efficiency of 99%;
sentences.translation: 在最佳条件下，螯合絮凝铜的效率达99%左右。

sentences.sentence: At the same time, the fluorescence lifetime of Eu3 + chelates was studied by using PMT and oscillograph.
sentences.translation: 同时，利用光电倍增管和示波器，研究了铕离子及其螯合物的荧光寿命。
